b_paragraph\" ><strong>Changing the radio music</strong> to fit your taste while fighting your way out </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss Fight mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric retro vibe</strong> that will make you feel like a 80s hero</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/1c59aee612dd0fc90b13912686e6eaba.poster.avif?t=1764323265\" width=800 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/1c59aee612dd0fc90b13912686e6eaba.webm?t=1764323265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/1c59aee612dd0fc90b13912686e6eaba.mp4?t=1764323265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
